
'''The Boy Who Harnessed the Wind''' ni filime yikinamico yo mu Bwongereza yo mu 2019 yanditswe, iyoborwa na Chiwetel Ejiofor<ref>The Boy Who Harnessed the Wind | Netflix Official Site</ref> . Filime ishingiye kuri memoire y'izina  na William Kamkwamba na Bryan Mealer<ref>The Boy Who Harnessed the Wind by William Kamkwamba ... <nowiki>https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com</nowiki> › books › the-b...</ref>. Yerekanwe mu gice cya Premieres mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance 2019 kandi itangira kunyura kuri Netflix ku ya 1 Werurwe 2019<ref>The Boy Who Harnessed the Wind movie review (2019) <nowiki>https://www.rogerebert.com</nowiki> › reviews › the-boy-who-h...</ref>. Yatoranijwe  muri Filime Nziza Mpuzamahanga Yamamaye mu bihembo bya 92 bya Academy, ariko ntabwo yatowe<ref>Netflix's 'The Boy Who Harnessed the Wind' is a True Story ... <nowiki>https://www.sandiego.edu</nowiki> › news › detail</ref>. 

