== Kurekurwa ==
Ku ya 14 Ugushyingo 2018, Netflix yabonye uburenganzira bwo gukwirakwiza ku isi, usibye Ubuyapani, Ubushinwa, n'Ubwongereza<ref>The Boy Who Harnessed the Wind (2019) - DVD Release Date <nowiki>https://www.dvdsreleasedates.com</nowiki> › movies › the-boy-...</ref>.  Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku isi mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Sundance 2019 ku ya 25 Mutarama 2019<ref>The Boy Who Harnessed the Wind (2019) - IMDb <nowiki>https://www.imdb.com</nowiki> › title</ref>.  Nyuma yaje gusohoka kuri Netflix ku ya 1 Werurwe 2019<ref>The Boy Who Harnessed the Wind · BIFA - British Independent ... <nowiki>https://www.bifa.film</nowiki> › film › the-boy-who-harnessed-t...</ref>.

